                       <br><a href="https://bit.ly/drhsieh_interview" target="_blank">觀看影片</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>《良醫健康網》專訪</h3>
                    <p>「止痛藥自己不吃，怎麼開給病人吃？」
                       <br><a href="https://bit.ly/drhsieh_interview2" target="_blank">閱讀文章</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>院長部落格</h3>
